    "body": "Currently classIDs< 2^56 are curated, meaning that the use of the ids should be submitted via PR to the core dev team.  If a user wishes to use an uncurated ID, they can choose a value >=2^56.    The register-oracle script should warn if a user attempts to register within the curated range.  check https://docs.verdikta.com/verdikta-common/CLASSID_USAGE_GUIDE/ for api calls to make the check.  ",
